    <item>
      <title>预计 2030 年香港私人财富资产将飙升至 2.3 万亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/hk-private-wealth-assets-seen-surging-to-2-3-trillion-by-2030</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博行业研究显示，香港管理的私人财富资产可能在六年内增长近一倍，达到 2.3 万亿美元，预计香港将超过瑞士，成为全球顶级跨境财富中心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/hk-private-wealth-assets-seen-surging-to-2-3-trillion-by-2030</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 03:36:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
