      <title>日本财务大臣就日元快速下跌发出警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/japan-s-finance-chief-gives-warning-over-yen-s-rapid-slide</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本财务大臣加藤胜信表示，日元兑美元汇率跌至近三个月来的最低点后，他正在提高监控汇率走势的紧迫性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/japan-s-finance-chief-gives-warning-over-yen-s-rapid-slide</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 03:17:31 GMT</pubDate>
